          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起三更鼓〗。张飞上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人情势利古今同，几个男儿是英雄。安得快人如翼德，要为汉室尽精忠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可笑袁术与俺打赌，明日生擒吕布。咳，你看咱的丈八矛在那里瞪眉弄眼，待\n俺磨洗磨洗。枪呵枪，你明日见了吕布，这么一枪，将那厮挑下马来，咱封你\n枪中王！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖风入松〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天色尚早，待老张打个盹儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起三更鼓〗。关羽、刘备同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岭岩鼓角三更尽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夜宿貔貅百万兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是三弟营盘，听他说些什么。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞醒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天呵，你是怎的不明，鸡，你是怎的不叫？呵，是了，想是吕布死期未到，待\n我再打个盹儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听三弟之言，战心太甚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待弟将他唤醒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不消，且待天明，我二人助他一臂之力。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有理。请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、关羽同下。〖起五更鼓〗。鸡叫。张飞醒，笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好了，天色明了，鸡也叫了，想是吕布死期到了，俺老张跨马快走。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖风入松〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，吕布小儿出关受死。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕布上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开关。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞杀吕布同下，吕布上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，方才关前来一黑汉，十分骁勇，他再追来，用花枪挑他下马。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里走！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕布杀，张飞败下，吕布追下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "张飞→刘备",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
          "edge": "刘备→关羽",
          "turns": 6
        },
        {
          "edge": "关羽→刘备",
          "turns": 4
        },
        {
