      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "关羽",
        "出此一枪走了罢",
        "刘备",
        "吕布",
        "张飞"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、关羽同上，两边望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟大战吕布，唯恐有失，你我催马助阵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。张飞上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟还是四弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "桃园。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还是杏园！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你与吕布交战，谁胜谁负？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我在前面走，这个娘养的在后面好追呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢是败了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，不错，是败了败了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你与袁术打赌一事，难道就忘了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀大哥二哥，看桃园份上，帮兄弟才好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢，你我三人，一马上，三马上，一马下，三马下。扣定连环，大战吕布便\n了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、张飞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥二哥随兄弟这里来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟到了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈，好彩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么彩头？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到取虎牢关，随兄弟这里来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急三枪〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到了关前，大哥二哥前去叫关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟前去叫关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我去叫关？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你去叫关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，这个王八厉害！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，为何不高声？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高声他不出来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原要他出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥二哥呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这作什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "桃园要紧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太小心了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，吕布小儿开关。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕布上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开关。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕布杀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我当是谁，原来是败将。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，你管我老子败不败，我老子又来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕布杀，张飞败下。刘备对锏，败下，关羽对刀，败下，张飞上，对抢。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀了半日，未曾问你贼名姓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕布我的儿，你问你老子名姓，咱姓张名飞，字翼德，自破黄巾以来，众诸侯\n闻名皆怕，吕布我的儿，你是怕不怕？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张翼德威名谁不晓，\n今日擒你献功劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞、吕布对枪，小钻盘。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕布敢是怯战？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是老爷怯战，敢与老爷下马赌力？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟，吕布下马，靴尖着地，有九牛二虎之力。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕布我的儿，你下得马来，有九牛二虎之力，咱老子下得马来，有七象八骆驼\n之力。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张飞，你认得你老爷？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺认得你，你是四姓家奴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟，他只有三姓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，大哥二哥，有所不知，他本姓吕，投与丁建阳，杀了丁建阳，投与董卓，\n俺弟兄灭了董卓，归了桃园，岂不是四姓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好匹夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一言怒发三千丈，\n胆大匹夫把我伤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "泗水关斩了华雄将，\n无名小辈敢逞强。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看锏！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "董卓残暴把君抗，\n重整汉室诛奸党。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四姓家奴休妄想，\n免得臭名万载扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "出兵会过多少将，\n三马连环怎能挡？"
        },
        {
          "character": "出此一枪走了罢、关羽、张飞、刘备",
